def is_prime(n: int) -> bool:
    if n < 2:
        return False
    if n < 4:
        return True
    if n % 2 == 0:
        return False
    i = 3
    while i * i <= n:
        if n % i == 0:
            return False
        i += 2
    return True
```

Checks divisibility by 2 once, then odd divisors up to sqrt(n); O(sqrt(n)) time.

